

text_1 = "It was a sunny morning for Captain Crazybones, sailing with his motley crew, when he finally found the treasure he was searching for. 'Ahoy!' He said, as he looked at the priceless gemstone on the distant island."
text_2 = "But reaching it wouldn't be without folly, as others were seeking the treasure as well, and there was no way that the Captain would let this fly."
text_3 = "Get inside, mateys! And keep a path to that island!"
text_4 = "'I'll deal with these scallywags myself!' It's time to fight for the treasure!"

